I have around 5.2 years of experience in Ruby on Rails, mainly working on backend APIs and scalable web applications.
In my current role I work with Rails 7, PostgreSQL, Redis and Sidekiq, building features like payment integrations (Razorpay), background services, and transactional email systems.
I also focus on performance optimization, writing clean code, and collaborating with frontend and product teams.

2. Explain one challenging feature you built.

You can talk about Razorpay integration.

Explain:

Problem

Implementation

Security

Edge cases

Example points:

Created payment service layer

