3. How do you handle performance issues in Rails?

Good points to mention:

Avoid N+1 queries (includes, eager loading)

Database indexing

Caching (Redis / fragment caching)

Background jobs using Sidekiq

Pagination

Query optimization

4. How do you ensure code quality?

Mention:

RSpec tests

Code reviews

Rubocop

Service objects / clean architecture

Logging & monitoring

